    <briefdescription>
<para>[Temporary] Apply a SplineBuilder2D to a <ref refid="classDerivField" kindref="compound">DerivField</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="classDerivField" kindref="compound">DerivField</ref> stores the values and the derivatives of a function. The inputs of the SplineBuilder2D are on different layouts than the fields we can get from the <ref refid="classDerivField" kindref="compound">DerivField</ref>. <ref refid="classSplineBuilderDerivField2D" kindref="compound">SplineBuilderDerivField2D</ref> allows to directly apply a stored SplineBuilder2D to a <ref refid="classDerivField" kindref="compound">DerivField</ref> by copying data in fields with correct layout.</para>
<para>Implemented only for 2D case. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
